result.name: Jack's Terrazza Ristorante

reviews.text: Very nice beer chicken. Extremely Tender and juicy. A must try item here. Must order beforehand. Buns that come before the dishes are soft and warm, served with very nice butter. Other dishes are good too. Very nice live singing on fri, sat and sun.  Good ambience, especially outdoor areas. A good Italian restaurant for both big group or just 2 people.
Awesome food, world class entertainment. State of the art hygiene. What more can you expect? This place is amazing!
Best part was the customer service. Food was barely adequate.

Excellent oasis amidst the hustle and bustle.
Great attentive service, good food, nice ambience, and go on Fridays, Saturdays, Sundays and Public Holidays to enjoy the top notch live music by Lorenzo, who's a complete encyclopedia in music. Pets welcomed as a bonus.
Prices reasonable & food was acceptable but really nothing special. Salad at the semi buffet was really sad, with the sesame salad sauce & garlic bread being the saving grace. Nice location though

reviews.text: 食物水準唔錯，部份餐連自助沙律吧，湯可再添，價錢合理。戶內外都舒服，招呼親切，擺單車同帶狗都歡迎。

Very nice beer chicken. Extremely Tender and juicy. A must try item here. Must order beforehand. Buns that come before the dishes are soft and warm, served with very nice butter. Other dishes are good too. Very nice live singing on fri, sat and sun.  Good ambience, especially outdoor areas. A good Italian restaurant for both big group or just 2 people.
看了評論四五星，食了羊扒丟了星，環境是好的，人氣不足，，傳統智慧，人少的食店咪入，圖片沙拉是靚嘢

某一天的假日，天氣非常好太陽🌤！老公帶我同阿仔去遊車河順便到大美督食午餐😎，超開心🥳
路過見到呢間西餐廳環境似花園又不用等位，就入左去食飯，由帶位到入內進食的員工(可能係老闆／經理）服務係非常細心體貼👍🏽👍🏽👍🏽👍🏽食物質素不錯又抵食!
對我來說，一間餐廳有冇心經營有質素食物最緊要就係睇「洗手間🚻」，係乾淨👍🏽有抹手紙👍🏽🤦🏽‍♀️阿仔突然爆💩片本想問職員我地可否一角的凳換片順便換埋衫，點知識員(高大4眼）提議去佢地洗手間🚻換片，洗手盆台面又真係幾長吓，啱啱免強放到阿仔上去換片😆⋯⋯真好彩🥰唔洗係出面換片餵蚊!
本身我都比較喜歡食西餐，所以有機會再來食飯！希望阿仔乖乖可以比我哋倆公婆切下排喇😁😄
Awesome food, world class entertainment. State of the art hygiene. What more can you expect? This place is amazing!
